{"tid":671282,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"全新瑪奇私服(G17S2版本)","createTime":"2018-05-20T04:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T04:06:09.000Z","uid":78617,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7f4715edb279723b48294e16589922f922ce3f8f","tid":671282,"uid":78617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T04:10:30.000Z","msg":"全新瑪奇私服(G17S2版本)<br />\nTG:<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEw30y4_SQWD-cZ4cg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEw30y4_SQWD-cZ4cg&d=z7vz%2BB42COkwiY3XNLusEE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=b369fae8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEw30y4_SQWD-cZ4cg</a><br />\n<br />\n全新既G17瑪奇私服五月開服半個月<br />\n常駐10倍任務經驗,任務金幣,技能修練,跑商<br />\n3倍探險等級提升,每日一轉<br />\n大部份實用技能,都改強左(穿心傷害,風車範圍加大等等)<br />\n<br />\nGMAE入面NPC有賣各種商城物品<br />\n高細,開孔,魔力賦予保護水等等<br />\n各種寵物骨龍,冰龍,水晶鹿都可以用GAME錢買<br />\n掛機有代幣,可以換指染,修練水,時裝<br />\n<br />\n有各種特色地下城,BOSS(使徒,黑龍白龍)<br />\n各種神卷(67層56層等等),黑白龍,使徒裝備,凱爾特材料圖紙)都有機會刷到<br />\n有惡魔地下城可以刷惡魔材料<br />\n<br />\n呢個SER時裝/物品貼緊官服(最新既深淵龍,櫻花禮服都有)<br />\n專用既染色系統,可以直接輸入色碼換指染<br />\n會陸續更新雙槍,忍者技能<br />\n<br />\n新入SER可以同GM拎新手禮包,服務<br />\n依家個SER夜晚既上線人數大約30~50人<br />\n雖然個SER係大陸SER,但係都有香港/台灣人<br />\n有公會系統,黎緊會開埋城堡房屋,公會戰,釣魚活動<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位想回鍋但係又無咩時間重新黎過/追唔返官服進度既玩家加入<br />\n玩開台服又想體驗下私服既都好歡迎!<br />\n<br />\n不過得網盤LINK<br />\n<a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1WqskeQku9TLey7gRg19pIQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpan.baidu.com%2Fs%2F1WqskeQku9TLey7gRg19pIQ&d=z7vz%2BB42COkwiY3XNLusEE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=bad27ada\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1WqskeQku9TLey7gRg19pIQ</a> 密碼：xhoe<br />\n如果下載得太慢,可以入TG借VIP<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/120117_2cbe5f8787d10055e23291e5dfd3bdef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F120117_2cbe5f8787d10055e23291e5dfd3bdef.jpg&h=36373549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/120141_a975e6c817d40df953aa826b3b6b4598.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F120141_a975e6c817d40df953aa826b3b6b4598.png&h=9c0595ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/120141_10af24c520aee0cb9ae0e64d0603cfca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F120141_10af24c520aee0cb9ae0e64d0603cfca.jpg&h=c4b68a92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"271629201ffec7d84a0eaf537fb8f8bd12a0afcc","tid":671282,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T04:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"be1d92ae639c90dc8b401d087d8fe0a6f387425f","tid":671282,"uid":78617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T04:16:40.000Z","msg":"由於注冊帳號要同GM直接注冊<br />\n所以要入QQ群:760645080<br />\n所有公告,資料都會係入面宣佈"},{"pid":"5ff0ff31187417a244a85418910b4957297bd71f","tid":671282,"uid":75754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"未玩過瑪奇 玩私服會唔會難上手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98b598bf456df734d2a8ca580955c6be8adfbfc4","tid":671282,"uid":78617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ff0ff31187417a244a85418910b4957297bd71f","tid":671282,"uid":75754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"未玩過瑪奇 玩私服會唔會難上手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T04:18:46.000Z","msg":"唔會,私服最適合起步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩唔明都可以係TG問"},{"pid":"e08fe1b2c989c7dd7fba55aaaa465bf23d3ca33c","tid":671282,"uid":7