EL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:10:26.000Z","msg":"講唔到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a040e7ea7ef07e0d61b329a77b949fe125a8fcc","tid":671282,"uid":140627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"快啲開啦ching"},{"pid":"e06b611097b9f281cfbaccb1165f8f7e81ca24f0","tid":671282,"uid":127145,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:13:00.000Z","msg":"認真 我係一個瑪奇玩左十年既人 中間斷斷續續都有回下鍋咁 又離坑咁 ， 但係望到呢個PO真心係有D心情唔好，依家其實已經對新手好好，無左以前咁難先至可以有好強既實力(累等未滿一千都好方便)，但係依家為左D野全部免費，或者屈住機咁打，所以玩私服，其實對瑪奇既玩家其實唔公平，真係唔希望推廌私服呢樣野，睇得出瑪奇依家都仲有比心機緊，人流都尚算仲有活人，要玩私服不如玩番大眾，如果係都要玩私服，都唔好推廌比人或者新手，我認會為曲解瑪奇吸引人既地方(自由同埋人情味)雖然我自己都明白香港代理垃圾，beanfun同低能一樣又難用又廢，但係瑪奇真係一隻好遊戲"},{"pid":"2a4674f002df987cf4be20982e53ee52f283e140","tid":671282,"uid":78617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:13:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EUDQIhE5QnxyVxHzyhxBNQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEUDQIhE5QnxyVxHzyhxBNQ&d=z7vz%2BB42COkwiY3XNLusEE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=f7436efa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EUDQIhE5QnxyVxHzyhxBNQ</a><br />\n<br />\n真TG<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}